  ('judicial-d4b276c4-moex-00002', 'judicial-d4b276c4', 'judicial-d4b276c4-moex-114-9140ce03', 'sub-judicial-d4b276c4-01', NULL, 'essay', '21 歲甲女為乙男收養之養女，甲女有三個月遭乙男監禁毆打，鄰居通報
